8... b6
{ This is Black's other plan if ...d5 does not work. But it won't be such a typical Hedgehog. }
9. f4 { This was played by some Magnus Carlsen guy. } 9... Bb7 10. Bd3 Rc8 11.
Qe2
{ This was Carlsen - Topalov, Nice 2009. Now Black should exploit his development lead with: }
11... d5 12. cxd5 exd5 13. e5 d4 14. exf6 Bxf6 15. Ne4 Bh4+
{ White's position is kind of a mess. } 16. g3
{ 16.Kd1  Re8  Black has various threats. } 16... f5 17. O-O Re8
{ White would do well to survive for a few more moves. } *

